constituent: younger sister, woman, not yet, one, tree, wood
heisigStory: The younger sister in the family is the woman in the family who, like the newest branch in a tree, is not yet old enough or mature enough to do everything the elder sister can do (See frame 442).
koohiiStory1: My younger sister is NOT YET a fully grown WOMAN.
koohiiStory2: Is your younger sister a woman? Not yet! Damn!
